<p><span class="anchor" id="p59"></span>قبض الْوَكِيل<a href="#p59" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p60"></span>صدق الْمُوكل ان كَانَ<a href="#p60" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p61"></span>الِاخْتِلَاف بَينهمَا<a href="#p61" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p62"></span>قبل تَسْلِيم الْمَبِيع وَإِلَّا<a href="#p62" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
